import pandas as pd --Example
data = {
    "Name": ["A", "B", "C"],
    "Age": [25, None, 30]
}
df = pd.DataFrame(data)
print(df)

df.isnull() --Missing value check

df.dropna() --Remove Missing values

df["Age"].fillna(df["Age"].mean(), inplace=True) --Fill missing values



Missing values ko handle karne ke liye:

dropna() → rows delete
fillna() → value replace
mean, median, mode se fill kar sakte hain
